      <Value><![CDATA[<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW87234716 BCX8"><strong>What do podiatrist do?</strong> <strong>They can improve, and even save lives!</strong></span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW87234716 BCX8"></span></p>
<p><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW87234716 BCX8">– podiatrists are trained to detect, prevent, manage and (at times) correct foot and lower limb problems. They can help to improve people’s health, support them to remain active, and even pick up more serious medical presentations which can ultimately save someone’s limb, and or their life.</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW87234716 BCX8"> </span> </p>]]></Value>
